        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>frames by function [300223194], frames (protective furnishings) [300189814], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
